{"tid":862014,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 將推出 iPhone XR 專用透明殼，盛惠 $330！","createTime":"2018-10-14T14:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T06:51:15.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"b67683d794364bb3079bb441352e9d5e20c2566a","tid":862014,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"Apple 官方一直有推出 iPhone 手機殼，雖然價格比較昂貴，但始終是原廠產品，依然有一批捧場客。最近有消息指 iPhone XR 正式推出時，將會同時首次加入官方透明手機殼，讓色彩選擇豐富的 iPhone XR 可以有足夠保護之餘，亦能展現特色。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Screenshot_2018_10_12_at_12.34.58-768x427.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FScreenshot_2018_10_12_at_12.34.58-768x427.jpg&h=f6c1472f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n據 Twitter 用家 IvaninCanada 透露，Apple 將會推出 iPhone XR 專用透明手機殼，售價為 55 加幣（約港幣 330）。這在 Apple 的官方 iPhone XR 新聞稿中亦有一句提及。有趣的是，在加拿大以外地區（包括香港）的新聞稿中，卻完全沒有提及這個新配件。這個透明殼將會採用硬膠還是軟膠材質製作依然未知。<br />\n<br />\niPhone XR 將會有 6 個配色選擇，加上玻璃機背，推出透明殼來讓手機設計展現出來，也確實是個不錯的選擇。不過透明手機殼設計簡單，坊間已經有大量的類似選擇，而且價錢只需十分一不到。到底透明手機殼會否在加拿大以外的市場推出，就要繼續觀察了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/14/apple-clear-case-iphone-xr/mobile-phone/phone-parts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2Fapple-clear-case-iphone-xr%2Fmobile-phone%2Fphone-parts%2F&d=GeeNnGMGm3oQLpY9yNG5uf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=322eb481\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/14/apple-clear-case-iphone-xr/mobile-phone/phone-parts/</a>"},{"pid":"985d5803a4cb66373569f196c8f11c442a85f15e","tid":862014,"uid":194606,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" 